**Your patron is [[[Noctra]]], the Arcane Genie, a mortal who achieved divinity through the obsessive study of magic and the arcane. Noctra is a god of magic, one who despises Mystra and her prioritization of order of knowledge. Noctra bends the weave to create pockets and folds hidden from Mystra's view. She recognizes that the combination of the arcane and the material plane creates a less "pure", but more permanent form of magic. She is the goddess of magic items and sanctuaries, physical places and items imbued with the power of the arcane. While she could never challenge Mystra's power with pure magic, her merging of the arcane and material have created something Mystra struggles to dispel.**

**Because of her mortal past, and recognition that her power only exists because of her knowledge of the vast variations of the arcane, Noctra is not monotheistic and in-fact encourages her followers to worship and study under other deities. Knowledge of the arcane in all forms is the greatest desire of all of her followers.**

